response.overview: "He genuinely loves his players. He genuinely loves Michigan. He is Michigan in so many ways." Joel Klatt -  I will miss Jim Harbaugh. I will miss his integrity. I will miss his authenticity. I will miss how he is a true leader who takes the bullets when it goes bad, but heaps the praise on his players when it goes good. I will miss all his sayings and quotes and how much he loves his players. There is no other coach like Coach Harbaugh. Thank you for everything.
response.title: Harbaugh: A Michigan Man
